highlights.text: Isac Elliot has the most spots on Top Songs Finland. “Ai Että” is the highest at #1.
“People's Champion (Vain elämää kausi 16)” by Lauri Haav is the highest new entry on Top Songs Finland at #2.
“Viimeinen tanssi” by Behm and Olavi Uusivirta has been on Top Songs Finland the longest, at 121 weeks straight.
“Feimii” by Lauri Haav and Gettomasa is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Finland, up 54 spots at #118.
